  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is a hot and cold buffet with freshly baked pastries, pancakes made to order, eggs, fresh fruit and cereal accompanied by freshly squeezed orange juice, coffees and teas.</p>
<p>The hotel's restaurant has large windows opening up onto the gardens. Dishes are carefully created using local and organic ingredients whenever possible (bookable and payable locally for Summer 23).</p>
<p>An elegant piano bar opens up onto the terrace with gorgeous views of the pool and gardens. </p>
<p><em>Please note that the hotel is bed and breakfast only for summer 2023. </em></p>]]></cateringDescription>
