  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The gardens of Hotel Simplon are stunning. There's around 20,000 square metres providing lovely walks, secluded spots and welcome shade in the sunshine. There's a large outdoor pool plus you can use the pools at the sister hotel. The centre of Baveno is within walking distance too.</p>]]></listingDescription>
