  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> have a traditional décor and can sleep up to three people. Facilities include air conditioning, TV, safe, minibar, hairdryer and a bathtub or shower. Rooms with a balcony and pool and partial lake view or full lake view are available for a supplement.</p>
